DPC_ObjectDetection_MemCfg DPC_ObjectDetection_InitParams_t::CoreLocalRamCfg

Core Local RAM configuration (e.g data TCM for R4F). DPC will allocate memory from this as needed and report the amount of memory consumed through DPC_ObjectDetection_PreStartCfg to the application.
